      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Inizio                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-out-str-out          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Protocollo                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "9"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      rf-ffx-num-prt       to   v-num                  .
